{"tid":1123254,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人眼睫毛倒生？","createTime":"2019-04-24T10:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T02:33:15.000Z","uid":5174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00b19dcd71a188f29cf7ac3696034cf79b442d24","tid":1123254,"uid":5174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"隻眼耐唔耐就痛，次次一照到見到有幾條毛係度dook住隻眼，要搵電筒強光照住先睇到，跟住自己搵拑拑走條毛。有時仲可能拑錯隔離，痛多幾野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者拑唔到連根拔起，只係係中間斷左仲衰，淨返短短既毛又拑唔到<br />\n有次又係咁，我自己拑完覺得都係睇眼科，點知個醫生話無事呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁又收我診金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想問下有無巴絲做過呢類型既治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網我見有咩電擊？同冷凍？又咩割眼臉/簾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303e3b980f52913c0b607f65540b8fadb15d3b64","tid":1123254,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"小手術，睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"d32abdb055e95c67525b7d92222f67adc6a9521e","tid":1123254,"uid":5174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"303e3b980f52913c0b607f65540b8fadb15d3b64","tid":1123254,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"小手術，睇醫生啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"上次睇個個眼科話我無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我都唔知點好<br />\n下次係咪要痛住都唔好自己拑，吉住咁搵醫生睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係又唔知係咪即日有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想睇下大家有無醫生推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2df38ab1249668b9cc5a2b1f03acea9f16be938","tid":1123254,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:25:14.000Z","msg":"有但係無理過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由佢甩先抹走佢"},{"pid":"a9ddd7c0c6b293f56446da1c6121ee9a46b078f8","tid":1123254,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"有，本身因為之前整親隻眼先會睇眼科<br />\n但好返之後再覆診，醫生就同我講我眼睫毛倒生<br />\n試過用激光整走個毛孔定唔記得咩啦<br />\n醫生個陣話激光個效果可以hold得耐啲<br />\n但我就無幾耐已經又倒生過<br />\n所以而家放棄了，由得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0fd32285db2c551706a43eaeb4b80eba52cd99","tid":1123254,"uid":5174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9ddd7c0c6b293f56446da1c6121ee9a46b078f8","tid":1123254,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"有，本身因為之前整親隻眼先會睇眼科<br />\n但好返之後再覆診，醫生就同我講我眼睫毛倒生<br />\n試過用激光整走個毛孔定唔記得咩啦<br />\n醫生個陣話激光個效果可以hold得耐啲<br />\n但我就無幾耐已經又倒生過<br />\n所以而家放棄了，由得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"原來咁濕9嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打而家係自己得閒拑走條毛？"},{"pid":"13c477b6479797aa172a861b3fa3d0477657cdf4","tid":1123254,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d0fd32285db2c551706a43eaeb4b80eba52cd99","tid":1123254,"uid":5174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9ddd7c0c6b293f56446da1c6121ee9a46b078f8","tid":1123254,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"有，本身因為之前整親隻眼先會睇眼科<br />\n但好返之後再覆診，醫生就同我講我眼睫毛倒生<br />\n試過用激光整走個毛孔定唔記得咩啦<br />\n醫生個陣話激光個效果可以hold得耐啲<br />\n但我就無幾耐已經又倒生過<br />\n所以而家放棄了，由得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"原來咁濕9嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打而家係自己得閒拑走條毛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"唔係，我由得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以時不時都會有野拮眼，唯有滴眼藥水"},{"pid":"2e7c77a5791ad574e3a2b2002d395808656bfbd4","tid":1123254,"uid":5174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}